    <h1>2020 — deferred to 2021</h1>
    <p class="page-lead">
      Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, the 2020 EISS Annual Conference was deferred. It was held at
      ISCTE-IUL in Lisbon on <strong>3 — 4 September 2021</strong>, in person and online.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

